query:
SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS from_company, MIN(lt.link) AS movie_link_type, MIN(t.title) AS non_polish_sequel_movie
FROM company_name AS cn,
 company_type AS ct,
 keyword AS k,
 link_type AS lt,
 movie_companies AS mc,
 movie_keyword AS mk,
 movie_link AS ml,
 title AS t
WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id
 AND ml.movie_id = t.id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
 AND mc.company_id = cn.id
 AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
 AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
 AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND cn.country_code != '[us]'
AND (cn.name LIKE '%TV%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Granada%')
AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
AND k.keyword = 'character-name-in-title'
AND lt.link LIKE '%s%'
AND mc.note IS NULL
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1938 AND 2006;
plan_content: /*+  SeqScan(ct) SeqScan(ml) SeqScan(lt) IndexScan(t title_pkey) IndexScan(mc movie_id_movie_companies) IndexScan(cn company_name_pkey) IndexScan(mk movie_id_movie_keyword) IndexScan(k keyword_pkey) HashJoin(ml lt) NestLoop(ml lt t) NestLoop(ml lt t mc) NestLoop(ct ml lt t mc) NestLoop(ct ml lt t mc cn) NestLoop(ct ml lt t mc cn mk) NestLoop(ct ml lt t mc cn mk k) Leading(((((ct (((ml lt) t) mc)) cn) mk) k)) */
